# Source Code Directory

This directory will contain your project's source code.

The structure will be customized based on your chosen language and framework during initialization.

## Common Patterns

### For Web Applications
```
src/
├── api/          # API endpoints
├── services/     # Business logic
├── models/       # Data models
├── utils/        # Utilities
└── config/       # Configuration
```

### For Libraries
```
src/
├── core/         # Core functionality
├── adapters/     # External integrations
├── types/        # Type definitions
└── index         # Main entry point
```

### For CLI Tools
```
src/
├── commands/     # CLI commands
├── lib/          # Core logic
├── utils/        # Helpers
└── cli           # Entry point
```